Then you all teach us

26
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:51,439
What should we do

27
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:53,680
Your Majesty

28
00:01:54,439 --> 00:01:56,000
It was Shi Feifan before

29
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:57,560
A blind cat caught a dead mouse

30
00:01:57,959 --> 00:02:00,319
Vice Minister of Revenue is so important

31
00:02:00,519 --> 00:02:01,840
He shouldn't get it at all

32
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:05,120
I have lived in Mou County for years

33
00:02:09,319 --> 00:02:11,479
Your Majesty, I believe

34
00:02:11,560 --> 00:02:13,280
Prince Qing is mistaken

35
00:02:13,439 --> 00:02:15,080
